title: MRGC Caddie Schedule for Sunday, June 3, 2018
content: Gentlemen,  Attached is the MRGC Caddie Schedule for Sunday, June 3, 2018:  May River Caddie Schedule Worksheet 6-3-18  We currently have 13 caddie jobs on the tee sheet with plenty of room for additions. Thanks for all the hard work this week and to those of you who traveled to help out PDC. Reminder we are closed on Monday and Tuesday for course maintenance so enjoy the days off.  Brian Lape
